dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, St_Croix_Addresses_2014.gdb. [The site address is a point feature class that locates situs or address locations]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use. For current data access please visit http://sccgis-scccdd.opendata.arcgis.com/
